dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. [Survey of Egypt]. In upper margin: Alexandria, scale 1:10,000. Sheet 3. Antiquities are located. This map was origiinally published by the Survey of Egypt and reissued by the U.S. Army Map Service in black and white in 1940; with designation: Map no. 3. Map Library does not have sheets 1,2,4 reissued in 1942 by U.S. Army Map Service. 1942
